===Etymology 1===
[[Image:Accetta.jpg|thumb|right|An axe]]
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|æx||lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*akwisī}}, probably from a {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*h₂egʷs-ih₂-||axe}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*h₂eḱ-||sharp, pointed}}. Compare German {{term|Axt|lang=de}}, Danish {{term|økse|lang=da}}, Icelandic {{term|öxi|lang=is}}, and also Latin {{term|ascia|lang=la}}.

